title: Newly Renovated 3 Bedroom/3 Bath With Panoramic Views !!!!!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-The Event Features a Demonstration Kitchen with Enough Room to Entertain a Few Close Friends or a Crowd', '-Large, private balcony with panoramic views', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', '-Stay Connected!', 'Wi-Fi in all Amenity Spaces', '-Over 20,000 Sq Ft of Amenities!', '-Brushed stainless kitchen faucet with pull-down sprayer', '-Well Equipped Tech Center with Mac and PC Computers and Multi-Function Printer', '-Pet Friendly Featuring Pet Spa and Bark Park', '-Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff', '-Quality-crafted cabinetry with under cabinet lighting', '-Large, Glass-Enclosed Indoor Pool, Sauna and Steam Room Open Year Round', '-Resident Portal: Enter Maintenance Requests Online when Convenient', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
